The WTB-plan, named for its primary supporters Woytinsky, Tarnow, and Baade, has been adopted as the unions' plan for getting us out of the depression. Woytinsky canvasses in favor of this policy through the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> and the unions.
